---
title: Roasted Pork Chops with Greens and Warm Sweet Potatoes
description: Tonight, you enjoy all the delicious flavours of BBQ without needing to fire up the grill! This soul-warming combo of roasted sweet potatoes, dressed greens and smoky BBQ sauce is sure to become your new favourite weeknight recipe!
